# Pull Request Creation Preference

When the user asks to create a pull request for this repository, use the GitHub Copilot MCP path first if it is available and authenticated.

Only fall back to `gh` when the GitHub Copilot MCP cannot perform the operation or is unavailable.

Before calling any MCP tool, read its tool schema/descriptor first.
